reviews.text:
I came to live with my child for a month. At first, rather than traveling and going to a new church, I only planned to hold services at the main church online. Then, I went there with the intention of giving it a go, but I gained strength from the good church members and the pastor's words, and my child met a friend at Sunday school, and it has been a happier month.
When I went to school with my church members on weekdays,
I also do rounding.
The child also goes to play on the soccer team.

7 minutes from Tiga

The pastor's words were good, and he was quite interesting..^^ The deacons also took good care of me, and I was very grateful. I was so sorry that I couldn't even say thank you because my child was sick.
I'm leaving this post in the hopes that you'll see this post. I am a mother who brought 2 elementary school students (boy and girl) and 1 girl from kindergarten. (I helped a little with meal preparation..^^;;) Anyway, although it was small in scale, it was a service with great grace.
I came here when I came to worship for a month in January this year, and I also came to worship for a month at the end of this year.

hello?
What time does Sunday service start?
Korean church located in Iskandar New Town, Johor Bahru
